children.name: Rules
children.text:
When this obsidian torc is placed around the neck it creates a cascade of sand-like bone fragments that spill over the shoulders and back like a cloak and vanish before they hit the ground. 
As a bonus action you can teleport to a space you can see up to 30ft away. After the cloak is used this way, opportunity attacks have disadvantage against you until the end of your turn. Once you use this ability it can not be used again until you finish a long rest.
